{
  "Vectors & Vector Operations": "矢量和矢量操作",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is the component form of a vector with initial point (1, 3) and terminal point (4, 7)?": "具有初始点(1、3)和终点点(4、7)的矢量的构成形式是什么?",
  "The component form is found by subtracting initial from terminal: ⟨4 - 1, 7 - 3⟩ = ⟨3, 4⟩.": "元素表通过从终端中减去首字母表示 4 - 1, 7 - 3 = 3, 4 = 3, 4 = 4 。",
  "What is the magnitude of the vector ⟨3, 4⟩?": "矢量的大小是多少? 3, 4, 4?",
  "The magnitude is |⟨3, 4⟩| = √(3² + 4²) = √(9 + 16) = √25 = 5.": "数量是 3, 4 = (32+42) = (9+16) = 25 = 5。",
  "If u = ⟨2, 5⟩ and v = ⟨-1, 3⟩, what is u + v?": "如果u = 2, 5 和 v = 1, 3, 什么是u + v?",
  "Vector addition is component-wise: u + v = ⟨2 + (-1), 5 + 3⟩ = ⟨1, 8⟩.": "矢量添加为构件:u+ v=2+(-1),5+3=1,8。",
  "What is 3⟨2, -1⟩?": "什么是3+2,1+1?",
  "Scalar multiplication: 3⟨2, -1⟩ = ⟨3(2), 3(-1)⟩ = ⟨6, -3⟩.": "Scalar 乘法: 32, -1 = 33(2), 3(-1) = 6, -3。",
  "What is the dot product of u = ⟨3, 4⟩ and v = ⟨-2, 5⟩?": "u = 3 , 4  和 v = + 2 , 5  的点产物是什么?",
  "u · v = (3)(-2) + (4)(5) = -6 + 20 = 14.": "□ v = (3) (2) + (4)(5) = - 6 + 20 = 14。",
  "Two vectors are orthogonal (perpendicular). What is their dot product?": "两个矢量是垂直的(垂直的),它们的点产品是什么?",
  "If two vectors are orthogonal (perpendicular), their dot product is zero: u · v = |u||v| cos 90° = 0.": "如果两个矢量为正向(直角),则其圆点产值为零: u □ v = u v cos 90° = 0。",
  "What is the unit vector in the direction of ⟨6, 8⟩?": "单位矢量向何方向 6 , 8 ?",
