  "If u = ⟨4, 3⟩ and v = ⟨1, -2⟩, what is u - v?": "如果u = 4, 33 和v = 1, -22, 什么是u -v?",
  "u - v = ⟨4 - 1, 3 - (-2)⟩ = ⟨3, 5⟩.": "-v=4 -1,3 -(-2)=3,5。",
  "A vector has magnitude 10 and direction angle 60°. What is its component form?": "矢量有等距 10 和方向角 60 度。 其成分形式是什么 ?",
  "v = ⟨|v| cos θ, |v| sin θ⟩ = ⟨10 cos 60°, 10 sin 60°⟩ = ⟨10(1/2), 10(√3/2)⟩ = ⟨5, 5√3⟩.": "",
  "What is a 'vector'?": "什么是\"维多\"?",
  "A vector is a mathematical quantity that has both magnitude (size/length) and direction. Examples include velocity, force, and displacement.": "矢量是一种具有数值(大小/长度)和方向的数学数量,例如速度、力和移位。",
  "What is a 'scalar' in the context of vectors?": "矢量的“ 梯度” 是什么 ?",
  "A scalar is a single real number with magnitude only (no direction). When a scalar multiplies a vector, it changes the vector's magnitude (and possibly reverses its direction).": "标量是一个只有星级( 无方向) 的单个真实数字。 当标量乘以矢量时, 它会改变矢量的大小( 并可能逆转方向 ) 。",
  "What is a 'unit vector'?": "什么是“单位矢量”?",
  "A unit vector has a magnitude of 1. It indicates direction only. Any nonzero vector v can be made into a unit vector by dividing by its magnitude: v/|v|.": "单位矢量的大小为 1, 它只表示方向。 任何非零矢量 v 都可以除以其大小 : v/ v , 制成单位矢量 。",
  "What is a 'resultant vector'?": "什么是“结果矢量”?",
  "The resultant vector is obtained by adding two or more vectors. It represents the combined effect, such as the net force when multiple forces act on an object.": "生成的矢量是通过添加两个或两个以上矢量获得的。它代表合并效应,如多重力对物体采取行动时的净力。",
  "What is the 'direction angle' of a vector?": "矢量的“ 方向角度” 是什么 ?",
  "The direction angle θ is the angle measured counterclockwise from the positive x-axis to the vector. It is found using tan θ = b/a for vector ⟨a, b⟩.": "方向  是从正x轴到矢量逆时针测量的角度。 它使用 tan  = b/ a 表示矢量 a, b 。",
  "A boat heads due east at 12 mph while a river current flows due south at 5 mph. What is the boat's actual speed (magnitude of the resultant velocity)?": "一艘船头在12米时向东飞行,而一条河水流在5米时向南飞行。 该船的实际速度是多少(由此而来的速度的放大速度)?",
  "The velocity vectors are ⟨12, 0⟩ (east) and ⟨0, -5⟩ (south). Resultant = ⟨12, -5⟩. Magnitude = √(144 + 25) = √169 = 13 mph.": "速度矢量为 12, 0(东)和0, -5(南)。结果 = 12, - 5。 磁度 = (144+25) = 169 = 13 mph。",
  "An airplane flies with a velocity vector of ⟨200, 0⟩ mph (due east) while wind blows at ⟨-30, 40⟩ mph. What is the resultant ground speed?": "飞机飞行速度为200, 0mph(东经),风吹在30, 40mph。 由此产生的地面速度是多少?",
  "Resultant = ⟨200 - 30, 0 + 40⟩ = ⟨170, 40⟩. Speed = √(170² + 40²) = √(28900 + 1600) = √30500 ≈ 174.6 mph.": "速度= (1702+4002) = (28900+1600) = (30500) (174.6)",
  "A worker pushes a box with a force of 50 N at an angle of 30° above the horizontal. What is the horizontal component of the force?": "工人在水平上方30°处推力为50牛顿的盒子。 横向部分是什么?",
  "Horizontal component = 50 cos 30° = 50(√3/2) = 25√3 N (≈ 43.3 N).": "水平成份 = 50 cos 30° = 50(__________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________",
  "Two forces act on an object: F₁ = ⟨8, 6⟩ N and F₂ = ⟨-3, 4⟩ N. A physics student needs the magnitude of the resultant force. What is it?": "F1 = 8, 6N 和 F2 = - 3, 4N. 物理学学生需要由此产生的力量的大小。 它是什么?",
  "Resultant = ⟨8 + (-3), 6 + 4⟩ = ⟨5, 10⟩. Magnitude = √(25 + 100) = √125 = 5√5 N.": "结果 = 8 + (3), 6 + 4 + = 5, 10 + 。 磁度 = (25 + 100) = 125 = 5. 5 N 。",
  "A soccer player kicks a ball with velocity ⟨10, 15⟩ m/s. The wind adds a velocity of ⟨2, -3⟩ m/s. What is the ball's actual direction angle (to the nearest degree)?": "足球运动员踢球的速度是 10, 15°C m/s。 风速增加速度为 2, -3°C m/s。 球的实际方向角度( 最接近的水平) 是什么 ?",
  "Resultant = ⟨10 + 2, 15 + (-3)⟩ = ⟨12, 12⟩. Direction angle = tan⁻¹(12/12) = tan⁻¹(1) = 45°.": "结果 = 10 + 2, 15 + (3) + = 12, 12 = 12, 12 = 方向角 = tan-1 (12/12) = tan-1(1) = 45°。",
  "A physics experiment measures two forces: F₁ = ⟨4, 3⟩ and F₂ = ⟨-4, 3⟩. A student needs to determine if the forces are perpendicular. What is their dot product?": "物理实验测量两种力量:F1 = 4, 3 和F2 = 4, 3。学生需要确定这些力量是否垂直。他们的点产品是什么?",
  "F₁ · F₂ = (4)(-4) + (3)(3) = -16 + 9 = -7. Since the dot product is not zero, the vectors are not perpendicular.": "F1 = F2 = (4) (4) + (3) (3) = -16 + 9 = - 7. 由于圆点产品不是零,矢量不是垂直的。",
  "A delivery drone must travel from point A at (0, 0) to point B at (6, 8) in a coordinate grid measured in km. What direction angle should it fly, and what is the distance?": "无人驾驶飞机从A点(0,0)到B点(6,8)必须在以公里测量的坐标网格中从A点(0,8)到B点(6,8)飞行。它应该飞向哪个方向角,距离是多少?",
  "Displacement vector = ⟨6, 8⟩. Distance = √(36 + 64) = 10 km. Direction angle = tan⁻¹(8/6) = tan⁻¹(4/3) ≈ 53.1°.": "迁移矢量 = 6, 8。距离 = (36+64) = 10公里。方向角 = tan-1(8/6) = tan-1(4/3)  53.1°。",
  "What does 'scalar multiplication' do to a vector?": "向量的“ 日历乘法” 对向量有什么作用 ?",
  "Multiplying a vector by a positive scalar changes its magnitude but keeps its direction. A negative scalar reverses the direction. The result is k⟨a, b⟩ = ⟨ka, kb⟩.": "将矢量乘以正弧值会改变其大小, 但会保持方向。 负弧值会逆转方向 。 结果是 ka, b = ka, kb 。"
